Ok since bullseye claims that we have some atention let's make a list for bullseye to send to them with BUGS(not things we don't like, we want, etc) if he would send it in that is(let's hope it fits the storyline to fix them  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"><P>1) When attacked by assassins out of stealth(with a PA attack) he does not autotarget, even if he did damage to me, i have to select him myself wich is kinda annoying<P>2) Same thing with archers, in most cases(not all) when archers shoot their intal shot at me(that bladeturn blocks) they do not become autotargeted and the pet does not attack them<P>3) This happens to me all the time, let's say i fail to mez a goborchend in emain where they are two linked together, i aoe mez, wait for a few seconds and charm one of them. The one i charm stays mezed but the one that is linked to the gobor somehow breaks mez and attacks me, with my pet mezed so there is not much i can do cept running. I've reported this and they said that they have never heard of this before, yet this happens to me EVERY time i aoe mez gobors and charm one, haven't tested on other mobs<P>4) When you put pet on stay and move a bit long away from it the pet status stops updating(if you put it on follow, it follows you but the screen still says that it's on stay, extremly annoying). Health stops updating as well.<P>5) General pet buffing issues, you all know them.<P>6) Getting interupted from a melee in combat mode 10 miles over the zone.<P>--------------------<P>Naev X lvl 50 Sorceress Prime of Pellinor<BR>Elza X lvl 50 Mercenary Master of Pellinor
